description:
3 Arrows Capital founders Su Zhu and Kyle Davies are battling each other on OX.FUN to see who will have a higher profit and loss (PNL).

This market will resolve to "Su" if Su Zhu's cumulative PNL (https://ox.fun/en/copy-trading/profile/102439) is higher than Kyle Davies's on April 20, 2024, 12:00 PM ET. This market will resolve to "Kyle" if Kyle Davies's cumulative PNL (https://ox.fun/en/copy-trading/profile/102409) is higher than Su Zhu's at that time. If these traders' PNLs are the exact same, this market will resolve 50-50.

The number used to resolve this market will be the cumulative PNL number (labeled PNL, under the trader's profile picture on their Master Trader profile page) when viewed.

The resolution source for this market will be information on Su Zhu's and Kyle Davies's respective PNL numbers on the check time according to their OX.FUN Master Trader profiles.
